    "created_at": "2011-12-08T18:53:44Z",
    "updated_at": "2011-12-08T18:53:44Z",
    "body": "Version is not hashed in order to permit backward compatible libraries to be upgraded without causing all dependant libraries to be recompiled. If the user wishes to force that they can change any extra link metadata tags.\n\nThis is a compromise between the desire to control and accurately reflect dependency, and the desire to do upgrades in the field the way os vendors prefer, using major.minor style versioning.\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
