    "updated_at": "2011-12-11T10:12:22Z",
    "body": "Another issue, for crates with different names and without extra meta data, they may end up the same hash. I think it would be good to use hash as a unique id when resolving crate dependencies. Actually, there are more than one FIXMEs about replacing the `cnum` with hash.\n\nIs there any background about not including crate name in hash?\n",
